---
title: Smoky Sloppy Joes with Pickled Red Onion, Shredded Carrot Salad, and Honey-Lime Vinaigrette
description: Get ready for a cafeteria throwback. We’re stepping up classic Sloppy Joes with pickled onion and deep, smoky spices. A crisp side salad and tangy dressing finishes off the dish with refreshing bite.
